{"parse":{"title":"International Society on Thrombosis and Haemostasis","pageid":32788867,"revid":756223391,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>International Society on Thrombosis and Haemostasis</b> (ISTH) is a not-for-profit global membership organization of specialists in the field of <a href=\"/wiki/Coagulation\" title=\"Coagulation\">blood coagulation</a> and its disorders, such as <a href=\"/wiki/Thrombosis\" title=\"Thrombosis\">thrombosis</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Hemophilia\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Hemophilia\">hemophilia</a>. It was founded in 1954 as the International Committee on Thrombosis and Haemostasis (ICTH). The society was reorganized in 1969 as the ISTH.<sup id=\"cite_ref-ISTHhist_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-ISTHhist-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> It currently represents about 4000 members from 93 different countries.<sup id=\"cite_ref-ISTHabout_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-ISTHabout-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> The society initiates and promotes education and outreach initiatives, research activities, scientific meetings, peer-reviewed publications, expert committees and the development of standards allowing a common language and approach to basic and clinical science all over the world. It also publishes a <a href=\"/wiki/Medical_journal\" title=\"Medical journal\">medical journal</a>, the <i><a href=\"/wiki/Journal_of_Thrombosis_and_Haemostasis\" title=\"Journal of Thrombosis and Haemostasis\">Journal of Thrombosis and Haemostasis</a></i>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Mission_statement\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Mission statement</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Scientific_and_Standardization_Committee\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Scientific and Standardization Committee</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Meetings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Meetings</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#ISTH_Academy\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">ISTH Academy</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Mission_statement\">Mission statement</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=International_Society_on_Thrombosis_and_Haemostasis&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Mission statement\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The mission of the International Society on Thrombosis and Haemostasis is to advance the understanding, prevention, diagnosis and treatment of thrombotic and bleeding disorders.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Scientific_and_Standardization_Committee\">Scientific and Standardization Committee</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=International_Society_on_Thrombosis_and_Haemostasis&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Scientific and Standardization Committee\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The Scientific and Standardization Committee (SSC) began in 1954 as the International Committee for the Standardization of the Nomenclature of the Blood Clotting Factors. The SSC is a permanent committee of the ISTH and is its scientific working arm. Conducted through 20 subcommittees and working groups, its activities promote cooperation among leading international scientists and direct their energies to projects that generate reliable and standardized clinical and basic science tools.<sup id=\"cite_ref-SSC_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-SSC-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Meetings\">Meetings</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=International_Society_on_Thrombosis_and_Haemostasis&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Meetings\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The ISTH hosts a biennial congress as well as annual meetings of the SSC. In odd-numbered years, SSC Meetings are held jointly with the congress.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Meetings_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Meetings-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"ISTH_Academy\">ISTH Academy</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=International_Society_on_Thrombosis_and_Haemostasis&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: ISTH Academy\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The ISTH Academy is the online education platform for the society. The ISTH Academy features webinars, webcasts, online courses and access to abstracts and posters from past ISTH meetings.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Academy_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Academy-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Publications\">Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=International_Society_on_Thrombosis_and_Haemostasis&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Journal_of_Thrombosis_and_Haemostasis\" title=\"Journal of Thrombosis and Haemostasis\">Journal of Thrombosis and Haemostasis</a></i>, official <a href=\"/wiki/Medical_journal\" title=\"Medical journal\">medical journal</a> of the ISTH</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=International_Society_on_Thrombosis_and_Haemostasis&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"reflist\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-ISTHhist-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-ISTHhist_1-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">ISTH (2015). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.isth.org/?page=History\">\"ISTH History\"</a><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2015-11-19</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=ISTH+History&amp;rft.date=2015&amp;rft.au=ISTH&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.isth.org%2F%3Fpage%3DHistory&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AInternational+Society+on+Thrombosis+and+Haemostasis\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-ISTHabout-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-ISTHabout_2-0\">^</a></b></span>